title: FURY PARK Featuring Thomas Krief
description:
French freestyle ski prodigy Thomas Krief takes on the monstrous and insane set up at the DC Area 43 snowpark at Méribel created by 7 shapers requiring over 1500 hours of hard work. 

All winter long, follow Thomas on TKTV webseries, which shows the backstage of freestyle and his performances on contests, as well as his preparation on his way to Sochi. 

Directed & Edited by Maxime Moulin

Music by Jonathan Cohen
